<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>[<span class="c2">(١٩٣)</span> حديث: <span class="c2">(الولد سر أبيه)</span>.]<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c2">(لا أصل له)</span> …<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c5">هذ الحديث على شهرته في أوساط الناس إلا أنه لا أصل له كما قال ذلك:</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c2">(١)</span> السخاوي في <span class="c1">"المقاصد"</span> <span class="c2">(ص: ٥٣٠)</span> رقم <span class="c2">(١٢٦٨)</span>.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c2">(٢)</span> السيوطي في <span class="c1">"الدرر المنتثرة"</span> <span class="c2">(ص: ١٨٦)</span> رقم <span class="c2">(٤٣٤)</span>.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c2">(٣)</span> الزركشي في <span class="c1">"التذكرة"</span> <span class="c2">(٢١١)</span>.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c2">(٤)</span> الصاغاني في <span class="c1">"الموضوعات"</span> <span class="c2">(٩)</span>.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c2">(٥)</span> ابن الديبع في <span class="c1">"التمييز"</span> <span class="c2">(ص: ١٨٧)</span>.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c2">(٦)</span> العجلوني في <span class="c1">"كشف الخفاء"</span> <span class="c2">(٢/ ٤٥١)</span> رقم <span class="c2">(٢٩١١)</span>.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span class="c2">(٧)</span> الفتني في تذكرة <span class="c1">"الموضوعات"</span> <span class="c2">(ص: ١٣٠)</span>.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span class="c2">(٨)</span> العامري في <span class="c1">"الجد الحثيث"</span> <span class="c2">(ص: ٢٥٣)</span> رقم <span class="c2">(٥٩٦)</span>.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span><span class="c2">(٩)</span> القاري في <span class="c1">"الأسرار المرفوعة"</span> <span class="c2">(٣٦٢)</span>.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span><span class="c2">(١٠)</span> القاوقجي في <span class="c1">"اللؤلؤ المرصوع"</span> <span class="c2">(٢١٦)</span>.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span><span class="c2">(١١)</span> الصالحي في <span class="c1">"الشذرة"</span> <span class="c2">(٢/ ٢٣٦)</span> رقم <span class="c2">(١٠٩٩)</span>.<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span><span class="c2">(١٢)</span> البيروتي في <span class="c1">"أسنى المطالب"</span> <span class="c2">(ص: ٣١٤)</span> رقم <span class="c2">(١٦٥٨)</span>.<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span><span class="c2">(١٣)</span> الصعدي في <span class="c1">"النوافح العطرة"</span> <span class="c2">(ص: ٤٤٢)</span> رقم <span class="c2">(٢٥٠٣)</span>.<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>